<subSubSection pageId="23" pageNumber="22" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="23.[192,1440,256,374]" pageId="23" pageNumber="22">
This group is characterized by having the mesosternum oblique between the mesocoxae. In North America it is known to contain only the genera 
<taxonomicName authority="Latreille" authorityName="Latreille." box="[740,937,287,311]" class="Insecta" family="Leiodidae" genus="Leiodes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[740,829,287,311]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="22">Leiodes</emphasis>
Latreille
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="Hatch. Baranowski (1993)" authorityName="Hatch. Baranowski" authorityYear="1993" class="Insecta" family="Leiodidae" genus="Ecarinosphaerula" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[993,1206,287,311]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="22">Ecarinosphaerula</emphasis>
Hatch. 
<bibRefCitation author="Baranowski, R." journalOrPublisher="Entomologica Scandinavica, supplement" pageId="23" pageNumber="22" pagination="1 - 149" part="42" refId="ref17927" refString="Baranowski, R. 1993. Revision of the genus Leiodes Latreille of North and Central America (Coleoptera: Leiodidae). Entomologica Scandinavica, supplement 42: 1 - 149." title="Revision of the genus Leiodes Latreille of North and Central America (Coleoptera: Leiodidae)" type="journal article" year="1993">Baranowski (1993)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
revised the North American species of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Latreille." box="[742,832,319,343]" class="Insecta" family="Leiodidae" genus="Leiodes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[742,832,319,343]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="22">Leiodes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. We here contribute new data on the genus 
<taxonomicName authority="Hatch." authorityName="Hatch. Baranowski" authorityYear="1993" class="Insecta" family="Leiodidae" genus="Ecarinosphaerula" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="23" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="22">Ecarinosphaerula</emphasis>
Hatch.
</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
